{"search_data": "Central PM Kisan Yojana 4th Installment to Beneficiaries with Aadhaar Linked Bank AccountsFor PM Kisan Yojana 4th Installment of Rs. 2,000, aadhaar linkage to bank accounts must for farmers, update / edit aadhar card no. at pmkisan.gov.inPM Kisan Yojana 4th Installment \u2013 Aadhar Linked Bank Account MustPM Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana was launched by Prime Minister Narendra Modi to benefit farmers. Under this PM Kisan Scheme, all the farmers will get Rs. 6,000 per year in 3 equal installments of Rs. 2,000 each as income support. Farmers can edit their aadhar details, check their name in beneficiary list and track application status at pmkisan.gov.in portal. The direct link to update aadhaar number details in PM Kisan Yojana by farmers is given below:- http://www.pmkisan.gov.in/updateaadharnobyfarmer.aspxThe page for editing aadhar details with PM Kisan Yojana will appear as shown below:-PM Kisan Yojana Edit Aadhaar DetailsFrom the fourth installment onward, payment would be made only to those farmers whose Aadhaar numbers have been authenticated with their bank accounts. Till date, the agriculture and farmers welfare department has authenticated more than 50 million bank accounts. The installment due between December 2019 and March 2020 is to be transferred to Aadhaar authenticated accounts.The date and venue for transfer of PM Kisan Scheme installment has not been decided yet. But the central govt. is prepared to disburse over Rs. 10,000 crore to farmers in one day. This may boost the rural economy at a time when GDP growth has hit ten bottom. All the farmers can now utilize this amount of Rs. 6,000 per annum for purchase of farm seeds, fertilizers, farm tools or other methods of their choice to raise their productivity.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/finance/now-pm-kisan-payments-only-via-aadhaar-linked-bank-accounts/articleshow/72432268.cms  at  "}